title: Opening
---
Opening:In 1601, Ireland is in the midst of the Nine Year's War, with most of the island's clans fighting off English forces under Elizabeth I. 
->Continue
The Tudors are determined to fully pacify the island, with English troops burning up any crops or livestock possible to starve the populace. 
->Continue
In the midst of this devastation, small communities did what they could to survive...
->Start
